data.value: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet version="1.0" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt" exclude-result-prefixes="msxsl" xmlns:user="urn:user"> <msxsl:script language="C#" implements-prefix="user"> <![CDATA[ public string PadPolicyNumber(string number) { return number.PadLeft(16, '0'); } public string SplitFLP(string value, int index) { string[] parts = value.Split(new char[] { '|' }, StringSplitOptions.RemoveEmptyEntries); return parts[index].Trim(); } public string ToUInt64(string value) { byte[] binary = Convert.FromBase64String(value); ulong ret_val = 0; for (int i = 0; i < binary.Length; i++) { ret_val <<= i > 0 ? 8 : 0; ret_val |= binary[i]; } return ret_val.ToString(); } ]]> </msxsl:script> <xsl:output method="xml" indent="yes"/> <xsl:template match="BarcodeData"> <xsl:element name="BarcodeData"> <xsl:element name="BarcodeType"> <xsl:value-of select="BarcodeType"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="PolicyNumber"> <xsl:value-of select="user:PadPolicyNumber(PolicyNumber)"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:if test="BarcodeType=1"> <xsl:element name="FirstName"> <xsl:value-of select="user:SplitFLP(FLP, 0)"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="LastName"> <xsl:value-of select="user:SplitFLP(FLP, 1)"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="Patronymic"> <xsl:value-of select="user:SplitFLP(FLP, 2)"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:if> <xsl:if test="BarcodeType=2"> <xsl:element name="FirstName"> <xsl:value-of select="user:SplitFLP(FLP, 1)"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="LastName"> <xsl:value-of select="user:SplitFLP(FLP, 0)"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="Patronymic"> <xsl:value-of select="user:SplitFLP(FLP, 2)"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:if> <xsl:element name="Sex"> <xsl:value-of select="Sex"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="BirthDate"> <xsl:value-of select="BirthDate"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="ExpireDate"> <xsl:value-of select="ExpireDate"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:if test="BarcodeType=1"> <xsl:element name="Ogrn"> <xsl:value-of select="user:ToUInt64(Ogrn)"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="Okato"> <xsl:value-of select="user:ToUInt64(Okato)"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:if> <xsl:element name="EDS"> <xsl:value-of select="EDS"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:element> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

data.name: BarcodeNormilizer
data.value: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet version="1.0" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt" exclude-result-prefixes="msxsl" xmlns:user="urn:user"> <msxsl:script language="C#" implements-prefix="user"> <![CDATA[ public string Concat(string FirstName, string LastName, string Patronymic, byte barcode_type){ return string.Format("{0}|{1}|{2}", FirstName.TrimEnd(), LastName.TrimEnd(), Patronymic.TrimEnd()).PadRight(barcode_type == 1 ? 56 : 68, '\x20'); } public string ToUInt64(string value, int MaxBytes) { value = string.IsNullOrEmpty(value) ? "0" : value; MaxBytes = MaxBytes > 8 ? 8 : MaxBytes < 1 ? 1 : MaxBytes; ulong vs = ulong.Parse(value); System.Collections.Generic.List<byte> ret_val = new System.Collections.Generic.List<byte>(); ret_val.AddRange(new byte[] { (byte)(( (ulong)vs & 0xff00000000000000) >> 0x38), (byte)((vs & 0x00ff000000000000) >> 0x30), (byte)((vs & 0x0000ff0000000000) >> 0x28), (byte)((vs & 0x000000ff00000000) >> 0x20), (byte)((vs & 0x00000000ff000000) >> 0x18), (byte)((vs & 0x0000000000ff0000) >> 0x10), (byte)((vs & 0x000000000000ff00) >> 0x08), (byte) (vs & 0x00000000000000ff) }); return Convert.ToBase64String(ret_val.GetRange(8 - MaxBytes, MaxBytes).ToArray()); } ]]> </msxsl:script> <xsl:output method="xml" indent="yes"/> <xsl:template match="BarcodeData"> <xsl:element name="BarcodeData"> <xsl:element name="BarcodeType"> <xsl:value-of select="BarcodeType"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="PolicyNumber"> <xsl:value-of select="PolicyNumber"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:if test="BarcodeType=1"> <xsl:element name="FLP"> <xsl:value-of select="user:Concat(FirstName, LastName, Patronymic, BarcodeType)"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:if> <xsl:if test="BarcodeType=2"> <xsl:element name="FLP"> <xsl:value-of select="user:Concat(LastName, FirstName, Patronymic, BarcodeType)"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:if> <xsl:element name="Sex"> <xsl:value-of select="Sex"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="BirthDate"> <xsl:value-of select="BirthDate"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="ExpireDate"> <xsl:value-of select="ExpireDate"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:if test="BarcodeType=1"> <xsl:element name="Ogrn"> <xsl:value-of select="user:ToUInt64(Ogrn, 6)"/> </xsl:element> <xsl:element name="Okato"> <xsl:value-of select="user:ToUInt64(Okato, 3)"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:if> <xsl:element name="EDS"> <xsl:value-of select="EDS"/> </xsl:element> </xsl:element> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
